  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wasted your whole weekend building a city? <br>We want to satisfy this idea of ​​building citys easily.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/f2302edbd911565afaaa9846a3fd79ed.avif?t=1735929619\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Mini Real Estate\" is a simulation construction game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We try to strip away the complexity of classic strategy games and combine construction and matching.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Mini Real Estate, you can build buildings to make them rise higher and higher to meet the color areas people want to go to</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/9e7bed5f64df978ce5f14b7639ec2564.poster.avif?t=1735929619\" width=230 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/9e7bed5f64df978ce5f14b7639ec2564.webm?t=1735929619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/9e7bed5f64df978ce5f14b7639ec2564.mp4?t=1735929619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the city continues to expand, new skyscraper combinations will bring different matching characteristics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need to frequently match the design relationship between buildings to achieve optimal efficiency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/130b1776e00f1aab84e570796dc76d9b.poster.avif?t=1735929619\" width=432 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/130b1776e00f1aab84e570796dc76d9b.webm?t=1735929619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/130b1776e00f1aab84e570796dc76d9b.mp4?t=1735929619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you find the right balance? Earn as many people and gold coins as possible for your city. Do you need more houses or taller buildings? More services, goods, jobs, or increased profits? The city is in a hurry, but nothing is more exciting than seeing a prosperous city that is successfully running well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/e206ac44a95ce59de1801c65868da748.avif?t=1735929619\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras_big/e206ac44a95ce59de1801c65868da748.avif?t=1735929619 width=800 height=800 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wasted your whole weekend building a city? <br>We want to satisfy this idea of ​​building citys easily.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/f2302edbd911565afaaa9846a3fd79ed.avif?t=1735929619\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Mini Real Estate\" is a simulation construction game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We try to strip away the complexity of classic strategy games and combine construction and matching.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Mini Real Estate, you can build buildings to make them rise higher and higher to meet the color areas people want to go to</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/9e7bed5f64df978ce5f14b7639ec2564.poster.avif?t=1735929619\" width=230 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/9e7bed5f64df978ce5f14b7639ec2564.webm?t=1735929619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/9e7bed5f64df978ce5f14b7639ec2564.mp4?t=1735929619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the city continues to expand, new skyscraper combinations will bring different matching characteristics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need to frequently match the design relationship between buildings to achieve optimal efficiency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/130b1776e00f1aab84e570796dc76d9b.poster.avif?t=1735929619\" width=432 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/130b1776e00f1aab84e570796dc76d9b.webm?t=1735929619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/130b1776e00f1aab84e570796dc76d9b.mp4?t=1735929619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you find the right balance? Earn as many people and gold coins as possible for your city. Do you need more houses or taller buildings? More services, goods, jobs, or increased profits? The city is in a hurry, but nothing is more exciting than seeing a prosperous city that is successfully running well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras/e206ac44a95ce59de1801c65868da748.avif?t=1735929619\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405200/extras_big/e206ac44a95ce59de1801c65868da748.avif?t=1735929619 width=800 height=800 /></span></p>",
